    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's primary known weak points. The engine retains its signature rasp, breathing through individual throttle bodies with precise throttle response across the powerband. Suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and lateral grip expected of the M-division's peak analog era. While the finish shows light patina from road use, the drivetrain is robust and the rod bearing clearances have been verified via recent oil analysis. A true driver\u2019s spec for those prioritizing mechanical integrity and performance dynamics.",
